                                <h6>Web server (HTTP)</h6>
                                <p><a href="http://localhost:8080">http://localhost:8080</a></p>
                                <h6>Web server (HTTPS)</h6>
                                <p><a href="https://localhost:7443">https://localhost:7443</a></p>
                                <h6>phpMyAdmin (HTTP)</h6>
